text: District 29 is a district of the Georgia State Senate. It comprises most of Troup County (including LaGrange), half of Columbus-Muscogee, and all of Harris and Meriwether. ==Senators== * J. Render Hill (1965–1984) * A. Quillian Baldwin, Jr. (1984–1992) * Steve Langford (1992–1998) * Dan Lee (D, then R) (1998–2004) * Seth Harp (R) (2004–2010) * Josh McKoon (R) (2010–2018) * Randy Robertson (R) (2018–present) Category:Georgia Senate districts
title: Georgia's 29th Senate district
